quran[12{c,v,t}:
16,43,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum se pehlay bhi jab kabhi rasool beje hain aadmi hi beje hain jin ki taraf hum apne paighamaat wahi kya karte thay ahal zikar se pooch lau agar tum log khud nahi jantay"
16,44,"pichlle Rasolo-n ko bhi hum ne roshan nishanain aur kitaaben day kar bheja tha, aur ab yeh zikar tum par nazil kya hai taakay tum logon ke samnay uss taleem ki tashreeh o tozeeh karte jao jo unn ke liye utari gayi hai, aur taakay log ( khud bhi ) ghhor o fikar karen"
16,45,"phir kya woh log jo ( dawat paighambar ki mukhalfat mein ) badter se badter chaalein chal rahay hain iss baat se bilkul hi be khauf ho gay hain ke Allah un ko zameen mein dhansa day, ya aisay gooshay mein un par azaab le aeye jidhar se is ke anay ka un ko vahm o gumaan taq nah ho"
16,46,"ya achanak chaltay phirtay un ko pakar le, ya aisi haalat mein inhen pakdae jabkay inhen khud anay wali museebat ka khatka laga howa ho aur woh is se bachney ki fikar mein chokannay hon ?"
16,47,woh jo kuch bhi karna chahay yeh log is ko aajiz karne ki taaqat nahi rakhtay haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab bara hi naram khoo aur Raheem hai
16,48,aur kya yeh log Allah ki peda ki hui kisi cheez ko bhi nahi dekhte ke is ka saya kis terhan Allah ke huzoor sajda karte hue dayen aur baen girta hai? sab ke sab iss terhan izhaar ijaz kar rahay hain
16,49,zameen aur asmano mein jis qader jaan daar makhloqaat hain aur jitne mulaika hain sab Allah ke agay sir bsjod hain woh hargiz sar kashi nahi karte
16,50,"apne rab se jo unn ke oopar hai, drtay hain aur jo kuch hukum diya jata hai isi ke mutabiq kaam karte hain"
16,51,"Allah ka farmaan hai ke"" do khuda nah bana lau, khuda to bas aik hi hai, lehaza tum mujhi se daro"
16,52,"usi ka hai woh sab kuch jo asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai, aur khalisan usi ka deen ( saari kaayenaat mein ) chal raha hai phir kya Allah ko chore kar tum kisi aur se taqwa karo ge ?"
16,53,tum ko jo Nemat bhi haasil hai Allah hi ki taraf se hai phir jab koi sakht waqt tum par aata hai to tum log khud apni faryadain le kar usi ki taraf dorrtay ho
16,54,magar jab Allah is waqt ko taall deta hai to yaka yak tum mein se aik giroh apne rab ke sath dosaron ko ( is meharbani ke shkrie mein ) shareek karne lagta hai
